Package: voice-transcription-tool
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-tk, python3-pyaudio, portaudio19-dev, xdotool, pulseaudio-utils
Recommends: sudo
Maintainer: Voice Transcription Tool Team <noreply@voicetranscription.local>
Description: Advanced speech-to-text application with AI integration
 Voice Transcription Tool is a modern, modular speech-to-text application
 featuring multiple recognition engines (Whisper, Google Speech), wake word
 detection, global hotkeys, voice training, and comprehensive GUI.
 .
 Key Features:
  - Multiple speech engines (Whisper local, Google Cloud)
  - Wake word detection for hands-free activation
  - Global hotkeys (Alt+D record, Alt+S settings, Alt+W wake word)
  - Voice training for improved accuracy
  - Auto-paste and clipboard integration
  - System tray operation
  - Modern tabbed interface with advanced mode
  - Audio feedback and device management
 .
 Perfect for transcription work, accessibility, and productivity enhancement.
Homepage: https://github.com/voice-transcription-tool
